Mordekaiser's got even more uproar than Cassi did, and still... silence. And considering the one who ~~trashed~~ reworked him is CancerlyT? That guy's one of the _most_ bullheaded Rioters. It must really suck, but it's very doubtful Riot's going to admit they made a mistake and revert Morde.
